Maintainer: Marta Azevedo <marta.vasconcelos4@gmail.com>
Description: The `survivalTB` package provides tools for interval-censored 
    survival analysis, including survival estimation, confidence intervals 
    via bootstrap, and customizable visualizations with base R and 
    `plotly`. The package is designed for researchers working with interval-censored 
    data in survival analysis, offering both efficient calculations and 
    interactive visualization options.
